snippet.textDisplay:
The whole "If force healing exists, why haven't we seen it before" is the same as "If Force lightning exists, why did noone use it in Episode IV or V"

The reason is, well, in both cases actually, that they are powers simply locked to the most powerful of either side of the force-spectrum.
I also choose to believe that force powers simply become more powerful as time goes on, because otherwise it'd be hard to justify someone as a specifically powerful force user, when you can always just point out how vader or Palpatine were better.
